cff-version: 1.2.0
title: >-
  cell-lookup-bench: a retrieval-free benchmark for table cell
  lookup in open-weight language models
message: >-
  If you use this benchmark or its results, please cite both the
  software and the accompanying article.
type: software
authors:
  - given-names: Dafa Farhan
    family-names: Haqiqi
